    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Users will only face a quadratic leak if the chain is not finalizing, i.e. at least 1/3 of validators are offline overall. Otherwise it is a small penalty, similar order to rewards.\r\n\r\nIt will only have a very small impact if it only happens for a few hours or a day. I generally agree that this could deter a few people from becoming validators, and I think the impact of allowing say 1 day of downtime per year would be very small. However, it's probably not worth the added complexity.\r\n",
